{
  "_meta": {
    "name": "evil-panda.strict",
    "label": "Evil Panda (LogicalTA) — strict",
    "description": "ATH + Supertrend entry, wide bid-ask dump play, evil_panda_exit layered exit. Screening tightened to bootcamp thresholds. Disables filter autotune loosening.",
    "source": "notes/METEORA_LP.md Bootcamp #7, evil-panda-bootcamp7-notes.md",
    "requires_min_wallet_sol": 2.25,
    "notes": [
      "minVolume 40000 assumes timeframe 1h (~$1M/24h Dexscreener equivalent).",
      "chartExitMinPnlPct still requires PnL > 0 before any chart exit fires (Meridian safety). Stop loss owns the dump path.",
      "deployAmountSol 2 → min free balance = deploy + gasReserve (2.25 SOL with gasReserve 0.25). Evil Panda bootcamp recommends 3 SOL for deeper fee share; 2 SOL is valid in Meridian."
    ]
  },
